Type: Package
Package: wisepocpac
Title: Wise POC PAC - Heat Pump Optimization Dashboard
Version: 0.1.0
Description: Interactive R Shiny dashboard for simulating and optimizing
    heat pump (PAC) control strategies with PV self-consumption,
    battery storage, and dynamic/fixed electricity pricing.
